				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I gave my character +10 INT at creation thinking this would net more mana/spell power.
<br />
Unfortunately, like everquest,I can't see the affect of my stats at all, other than obvious things like STR and encumberance.
<br />

<br />
page 40 of the manual says: "All 'intelligence' based casters (wizard, theurgist, cabalist, sorcerer, eldritch, enchanter, mentalist) get the Quick Cast ability."
<br />

<br />
Nightshade is not listed.  I wonder how Nightshade mana is calculated?
<br />

<br />
Please read my post on the general forum about defining what character STATs are for.
