				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I hope you didn't get too much time in on your char, that 10 int was probably not a good idea.  NS never run out of power, so having more is pretty trivial.  On the other hand they really need dex, quick, const, and str.  If you play a shorty, you can have an awesome set of stats.  Stats affect everything in the game, so having more points in critical stats is very important.  It's not like EQ where you see little difference in ability when you have 100 pts difference.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
